<%- include('partials/header', { currentPage: 'rules' }) %>

<div class="page">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:760px">

    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-title">📋 Competition Rules</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">

      <div class="rules-section">
        <h3>🎯 How to Play</h3>
        <p style="font-size:.9rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.8">
          Predict the outcome of every FIFA World Cup 2026 match. For each match, select the winning team (or Draw in group stage).
          In knockout rounds, also predict whether the match ends in 90 minutes or goes to AET/Penalties for a bonus point.
          Earn points for correct predictions and compete with your friends on the leaderboard!
        </p>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider">

      <div class="rules-section">
        <h3>⚽ Group Stage (72 matches)</h3>
        <p style="font-size:.9rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:12px">Choose: <strong>Team A Win</strong> · <strong>Draw</strong> · <strong>Team B Win</strong></p>
        <table class="rules-table">
          <thead><tr><th>Outcome</th><th>Points</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>✅ Correct prediction</td><td><strong style="color:var(--gold)">1 point</strong></td></tr>
            <tr><td>❌ Wrong prediction</td><td>0 points</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Maximum group stage total</td><td><strong style="color:var(--gold)">72 points</strong></td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider">

      <div class="rules-section">
        <h3>🏆 Knockout Stage</h3>
        <p style="font-size:.9rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:12px">
          Choose the <strong>winning team</strong> (no draws). Also predict: <strong>90 Minutes</strong> or <strong>AET/Penalties</strong> for a bonus point.
          Bonus is only awarded if you also correctly predicted the winner.
        </p>
        <table class="rules-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Round</th>
              <th>Correct Winner</th>
              <th>AET Bonus</th>
              <th>Max per match</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Round of 32</td><td><strong style="color:var(--gold)">2 pts</strong></td><td>+1 pt</td><td>3 pts</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Round of 16</td><td><strong style="color:var(--gold)">3 pts</strong></td><td>+1 pt</td><td>4 pts</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Quarterfinals</td><td><strong style="color:var(--gold)">4 pts</strong></td><td>+1 pt</td><td>5 pts</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Semifinals</td><td><strong style="color:var(--gold)">5 pts</strong></td><td>+1 pt</td><td>6 pts</td></tr>
            <tr><td>3rd Place Match</td><td><strong style="color:var(--gold)">4 pts</strong></td><td>+1 pt</td><td>5 pts</td></tr>
            <tr><td>⭐ Final</td><td><strong style="color:var(--gold)">6 pts</strong></td><td>+1 pt</td><td>7 pts</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider">

      <div class="rules-section">
        <h3>🔒 Prediction Locks</h3>
        <p style="font-size:.9rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.8">
          The admin will lock predictions before each match or round begins. Once locked, you cannot change your prediction.
          Make sure to submit early! You can edit your prediction at any time before the lock.
          Locked predictions are final — no exceptions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider">

      <div class="rules-section" style="margin-bottom:0">
        <h3>🕐 Times</h3>
        <p style="font-size:.9rem;color:var(--text-dim);line-height:1.8">
          All match times on this platform are displayed in <strong style="color:var(--text)">Kuwait Time (UTC+3)</strong>.
          Make sure to submit predictions before kickoff time shown on each match card.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
